title: p53 and MDM2 Dynamic Systems Simulation
description: This small  python module was written to model the simplified dynamics of p53 autoregulation and ubiquitation by MDM2. It was written for Professor Jeff Hasty's BENG125 during Spring 2025.

title: BENG Senior Design Project: Designer TM Channels
description: De novo design of transmembrane proton channels with soluble domain linkers. We aimed to stabalize an adapted Cl-/H+ antiport mechanism in a self-assembling, homooligomeric, minimal transmembrane pore. Presented at BMES @ UCSD 2025 BE Day

title: MitoLysate
description: For developing rapid cryoEM workflows. Determine high-resolution structures within a week.

title: DSC106 Visualizations
description: Exploratory visualizations of datasets regarding processed groceries, economic indicators of climate change etc. to practice effective visual encodings.
